==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blameful
<hw>Blame"ful</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Faulty; meriting blame.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Attributing blame or fault; implying or conveying
censure; faultfinding; censorious.</def> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Blame"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Blame"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blameless</ent>⟦br⟧
